Interface Path<V>

  • Type Parameters:
    V - the generic type of the property value identified by this path.
    All Superinterfaces:
    Argument<V>, AttributeReadName, AttributeReadValue<V>, PathFactory, PropertyPath<V>
    All Known Subinterfaces:

    public interface Path<V>
extends PathFactory, PropertyPath<V>, Argument<V>
